description:
Stealing a headband from a kid at a football game is about as lame as it gets, and thats exactly what this TikToker is defending doing as we speak. Today, we look at Nina Miller, who has recently gone under fire for taking Patrick Mahome's headband out of a kids hand at a Chief's game.
